text: Sergio Giavanni Kitchens (born June 14, 1993), known professionally as Gunna, is an American rapper and singer. He is signed to Young Thug's record label YSL Records, as well as 300 Entertainment and Atlantic Records. He released his first studio album, Drip or Drown 2, in 2019. His second studio album Wunna followed in 2020. It debuted at number one on the Billboard 200. His third album DS4Ever was released in 2022, becoming his second number one album. == Awards and nominations == Award Year Nominee Category Result Ref.
